I'm sure Eliza wouldn't

00:27:29.410 --> 00:27:32.440
mind shaking your hand
and trying to be bribed.

00:27:32.440 --> 00:27:34.530
For the next one--
the next prize

00:27:34.530 --> 00:27:36.470
that I'm going to describe,
if you are tempted

00:27:36.470 --> 00:27:42.740
to for any reason, to applaud
this achievement, please

00:27:42.740 --> 00:27:43.360
do not.

00:27:43.360 --> 00:27:46.780
Please just hold your
applause on this one

00:27:46.780 --> 00:27:48.900
no matter how much you
approve, or whatever,

00:27:48.900 --> 00:27:50.830
of what this person did.

00:27:50.830 --> 00:27:54.420
The Ig Nobel Peace
Prize was awarded

00:27:54.420 --> 00:27:57.657
to Alexander Lukashenko,
the President

00:27:57.657 --> 00:27:58.740
of the country of Belarus.

00:28:00.320 --> 00:28:03.540
He won the Ig Nobel
Peace Prize for making

00:28:03.540 --> 00:28:06.325
it illegal to applaud in public.

00:28:07.610 --> 00:28:12.430
He shared the Peace Prize
with the Belarus State Police,

00:28:12.430 --> 00:28:15.775
who were arrested a
one-armed man for applauding.

00:28:17.990 --> 00:28:22.040
Here are some of President
Lukashenko's press clippings

00:28:22.040 --> 00:28:23.010
from around the world.

00:28:25.577 --> 00:28:27.410
We gave a prize in the
field of Probability.

00:28:28.460 --> 00:28:31.350
That Ig Nobel Prize
was awarded to a team

00:28:31.350 --> 00:28:34.420
from the UK, the
Netherlands, and Canada.

00:28:34.420 --> 00:28:36.410
They're based in
Edinburgh in Scotland.

00:28:38.020 --> 00:28:41.560
They won for making two
related discoveries.

00:28:41.560 --> 00:28:47.310
First, that the longer a
cow has been lying down,

00:28:47.310 --> 00:28:49.790
the more likely that
cow will soon stand up.

00:28:49.790 --> 00:28:51.870
[LAUGHTER]

00:28:51.870 --> 00:28:56.570
And second, that
once a cow stands up,

00:28:56.570 --> 00:28:59.236
you cannot easily predict how
soon the cow will lie down

00:28:59.236 --> 00:28:59.735
again.

00:29:01.360 --> 00:29:04.640
They published a paper called
"Are Cows More Likely to Lie

00:29:04.640 --> 00:29:09.256
Down the Longer They Stand?"

00:29:09.256 --> 00:29:11.860
They sent us this
photo of the research.

00:29:13.090 --> 00:29:15.710
And this is Bert Tolkamp,
one of the researchers

00:29:15.710 --> 00:29:18.310
who flew from
Edinburgh to Cambridge

00:29:18.310 --> 00:29:22.470
here to hastily finish
up his acceptance speech

00:29:22.470 --> 00:29:23.220
as you can see.

00:29:24.510 --> 00:29:27.690
And the Ig Nobel Prize
for Public Health

00:29:27.690 --> 00:29:31.760
was awarded to a large team
of doctors in Thailand.

00:29:31.760 --> 00:29:33.850
They're all based
at the same hospital

00:29:33.850 --> 00:29:36.090
in the city of
Bangkok, Thailand.

00:29:36.090 --> 00:29:38.930
They were honored for
the medical techniques

00:29:38.930 --> 00:29:41.850
they described in a
report they published.

00:29:41.850 --> 00:29:44.760
Their report is called
"Surgical Management

00:29:44.760 --> 00:29:50.586
of an Epidemic of Penile
Amputations in Siam."

00:29:50.586 --> 00:29:52.830
A "Surgical Management
of an Epidemic

00:29:52.830 --> 00:29:56.410
of Penile Amputations in Siam."

00:29:56.410 --> 00:29:59.220
They were honored for
those techniques which

00:29:59.220 --> 00:30:05.230
they recommend, except in cases
where the amputated penis has

00:30:05.230 --> 00:30:08.550
been partially eaten by a duck.

00:30:08.550 --> 00:30:11.350
[LAUGHTER]

00:30:11.350 --> 00:30:15.406
Here is the beginning of their
paper, which, as you can see,

00:30:15.406 --> 00:30:17.780
sure enough is called "Surgical
Management of an Epidemic

00:30:17.780 --> 00:30:20.920
of Penile Amputations in Siam."

00:30:20.920 --> 00:30:25.110
I would be happy to explain
the duck part if you like.

00:30:25.110 --> 00:30:27.650
And if you already
know, that's fine

00:30:27.650 --> 00:30:29.810
and I won't waste your time.

00:30:30.665 --> 00:30:31.165
Anybody?

00:30:32.332 --> 00:30:33.364
AUDIENCE: Do tell.

00:30:33.364 --> 00:30:34.405
MARC ABRAHAMS: All right.

00:30:35.710 --> 00:30:38.270
There's always one person
who somehow has not

00:30:38.270 --> 00:30:39.340
heard the details.

00:30:41.160 --> 00:30:43.710
As they explain,
I think lovingly

00:30:43.710 --> 00:30:48.480
in this paper for the benefit
of readers outside Thailand,

00:30:48.480 --> 00:30:51.170
in Thailand many
people live in houses

00:30:51.170 --> 00:30:52.720
that are built on stilts.

00:30:54.540 --> 00:30:58.720
And many of those houses--
underneath the house,

00:30:58.720 --> 00:31:03.835
the family keeps the farm
animals-- chickens, ducks,

00:31:03.835 --> 00:31:04.335
whatever.

00:31:05.730 --> 00:31:09.430
There was during the
1970s a true epidemic.

00:31:09.430 --> 00:31:14.390
Apparently the first one or
two were publicized heavily

00:31:14.390 --> 00:31:16.200
in the newspapers
and this somehow led

00:31:16.200 --> 00:31:21.070
to many other people doing
it of angry wives severing

00:31:21.070 --> 00:31:22.030
their husband's penis.

00:31:23.320 --> 00:31:25.840
Usually, after the
husband had done

00:31:25.840 --> 00:31:31.210
much provoking of some sort
the wife would sever the penis.

00:31:31.210 --> 00:31:33.445
And then sometimes,
throw it out the window.

00:31:34.480 --> 00:31:36.900
And occasionally,
the severed penis,

00:31:36.900 --> 00:31:38.430
in its journey
outside the window,

00:31:38.430 --> 00:31:42.510
would land down amidst
the farm animals, which

00:31:42.510 --> 00:31:45.040
wasn't necessarily
a terrible problem

00:31:45.040 --> 00:31:46.670
as far as the surgeons
were concerned.

00:31:46.670 --> 00:31:49.150
They were usually able
to reattach the pieces

00:31:49.150 --> 00:31:50.770
and get everything working.

00:31:50.770 --> 00:31:55.390
Except, they said, in cases
where the piece of meat

00:31:55.390 --> 00:31:57.900
had been chewed by a duck.

00:31:57.900 --> 00:32:00.120
So was that clear?

