And if you write a
book, you're always

00:32:49.770 --> 00:32:51.540
grateful when you
get a long review

00:32:51.540 --> 00:32:53.910
because there's not that
much space in newspapers.

00:32:53.910 --> 00:32:57.390
This was in the biggest
of the London newspapers,

00:32:57.390 --> 00:33:00.370
"The Daily Mail,"
