00:33:04.170 --> 00:33:05.180
and many other things.

00:33:05.180 --> 00:33:08.190
But they gave it a long review.

00:33:08.190 --> 00:33:11.630
And what I'm proud of
is that they summed up

00:33:11.630 --> 00:33:14.030
the book in the midst of
that review in this phrase.

00:33:14.030 --> 00:33:16.867
They said that this book
is almost dementedly

00:33:16.867 --> 00:33:17.533
inconsequential.

00:33:21.940 --> 00:33:26.080
So I hope you enjoy the
book and the other things

00:33:26.080 --> 00:33:28.630
I'll be writing about.

